Uses of Package
com.imkrisna.samsung.nservice

  • Classes in com.imkrisna.samsung.nservice used by com.imkrisna.samsung.nservice 
    Class and Description
    NSConnection
    This class is the main process for com.imkrisna.samsung.nservice library for android.
    NSDevice
    This class represents single N-Service capable device.
    NSDiscovery
    This class is helper to find N-Service capable devices (NSDevice) using SSDP Packet listener from com.cyabergarage.upnp.ssdp.
    NSDiscovery.NSDiscoveryListener
    This class implementing SearchResponseListener is a response handler for incoming SSDPPacket and parsing the information to decide whether the devices is N-Service capable device or not then storing the capable devices to NSConnection instance.
    NSListener
    This class extending android Activity class.
